items.summary:
*Nidec Corporation has adopted Siemens' Teamcenter X to enhance electric motor development.*
- The software integrates Product Lifecycle Management (PLM) and Quality Management System (QMS) to improve traceability, configuration, and quality assurance.
- This digital transformation aims to boost innovation, efficiency, and quality in motor manufacturing, especially for automotive applications.**

